column1: # Name: Real GDP (US$ at PPP, 2005 prices)
# Definition: Gross domestic product (GDP) at constant market prices, rebased to 2005 constant prices and translated into US$ (in billions) using the LCU:$ PPP exchange rate in 2005.
# Data from the No Ceilings project: http://noceilings.org
# For more about the data, please visit http://noceilings.org/data
